verifier.ast

Class ASTFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • verifier.ast.ASTFactory
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ComparisonFactory, ListArgFactory, PQuantifierFactory, PrimFactory, QuantifierFactory

    public abstract class ASTFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Each type of AST node must define a corresponding factory. The factory is used by the parser to construct instances of the given AST type. AST factories are the means by which primitives are pluggable -- plugins provide the parser with factories in order to add support for new primitive types.
